00:00 NEW MOVIE NEWS 2025 & 2026 
00:30 Avengers Doomsday Trailer
Marvel fans are in for a possible early treat as the first trailer for Avengers: Doomsday may soon be released. Reports suggest the trailer could premiere in theaters alongside the upcoming Avatar: Fire and Ash, which is set to hit cinemas in December 2025. 
01:41 The Mummy 
Brendan Fraser is officially returning to the big screen as part of a new The Mummy movie, exciting fans of the original series.The new Mummy movie is being produced by Universal Pictures as part of their continued efforts to revive classic franchises. 
02:58 Jurassic World Rebirth 2
Big things are in motion for the Jurassic World: Rebirth franchise. Gareth Edwards, who directed the 2025 reboot, is reportedly in final talks to return for its follow‑up, which would continue the story introduced in Rebirth. The new film is expected to hit theaters in June 2028, with key cast members already linked to return.
